## 🔧 **테스트 명령어**

### **YouTube URL 테스트**
```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:8080/api/vdp/universal \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "url": "https://www.youtube.com/shorts/aX5y8wz60ws",
    "platform": "youtube"
  }'
```

### **TikTok URL 테스트**
```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:8080/api/vdp/universal \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "url": "https://www.tiktok.com/@lovedby4bxnia/video/7529657626947374349",
    "platform": "tiktok"
  }'
```

### **Instagram URL 테스트**
```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:8080/api/vdp/universal \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "url": "https://www.instagram.com/reel/DLx4668NGGv/",
    "platform": "instagram"
  }'
```

